You didn't miss anything.

153
00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:58,266
CROWD:
Oh!

154
00:12:58,441 --> 00:13:01,376
- Come on, Collins, move your feet.
SEAN: Good job, Collins.

155
00:13:01,544 --> 00:13:02,636
Go.

156
00:13:06,683 --> 00:13:07,945
We'll wait for you outside.

157
00:13:08,118 --> 00:13:10,678
Don't double condition in
the shower, you have homework.

158
00:13:10,854 --> 00:13:12,321
I'm going to Cannon's to study.

159
00:13:12,489 --> 00:13:17,950
SJ! SJ, do not go in the girls' locker
room again. Come here! SJ, come here!

160
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:33,675
<i>MAN: The big kid's been here
for, what, a month?</i>

161
00:13:34,077 --> 00:13:35,977
He's still not cutting it in my class.

162
00:13:36,146 --> 00:13:39,843
Why does Admissions do this?
I mean, it's not fair to us or the boy.

163
00:13:40,016 --> 00:13:41,677
They're just setting him up to fail.

164
00:13:41,851 --> 00:13:44,183
I don't think he has any idea
of what I'm teaching.

165
00:13:44,354 --> 00:13:46,845
And how would you know if he did?
He won't even talk.

166
00:13:47,824 --> 00:13:48,848
He writes.

167
00:13:49,025 --> 00:13:50,925
His name. Barely.

168
00:13:52,095 --> 00:13:54,655
He threw this in the trash can.

169
00:13:58,368 --> 00:14:01,201
"I look and I see white everywhere:

170
00:14:01,371 --> 00:14:06,536
White walls, white floors,
and a lot of white people.

171
00:14:06,876 --> 00:14:12,143
The teachers do not know I have no idea
of anything they are talking about.

172
00:14:12,315 --> 00:14:15,375
I do not wanna listen to anyone,
especially the teachers.

173
00:14:15,552 --> 00:14:20,512
