767
00:57:34,081 --> 00:57:36,072
Excuse me.

768
00:57:37,284 --> 00:57:38,876
I'm not cutting, I'm just asking.

769
00:57:39,053 --> 00:57:42,716
Let me tell you something. We have been
sitting around here for over an hour...

770
00:57:42,890 --> 00:57:47,122
...and when I look around and all I see are
people shooting the bull and drinking coffee.

771
00:57:47,294 --> 00:57:48,488
Who runs this place?

772
00:57:51,765 --> 00:57:54,325
I'd have it in shape in two days,
I can tell you that.

773
00:57:54,501 --> 00:57:57,561
- I bet you would. How can I help you?
- Oh, he was first.

774
00:57:57,738 --> 00:58:01,037
- No, you go ahead. I think I wanna hear this.
- Me too.

775
00:58:01,208 --> 00:58:02,937
I do not appreciate the attitude.

776
00:58:03,110 --> 00:58:05,908
Ma'am, now, you can tell me
what you want...

777
00:58:06,080 --> 00:58:08,275
...or I can make sure
you wait here all day.

778
00:58:08,449 --> 00:58:09,939
Now, how can I help you?

779
00:58:10,317 --> 00:58:12,217
I would like to become a legal guardian.

780
00:58:12,486 --> 00:58:14,681
Lord help that child.

781
00:58:18,258 --> 00:58:22,592
There's very little on Michael.
Most of his files have been lost.

782
00:58:22,763 --> 00:58:25,755
- Well, what is in there?
- A few case notes.

783
00:58:26,300 --> 00:58:30,760
This one describes an incident where
officers forcibly removed Michael...

784
00:58:30,938 --> 00:58:33,668
...from Denise Oher's care
when Michael was 7.

785
00:58:33,841 --> 00:58:36,639
Quite a scene evidently.
They had to split up the kids.

786
00:58:36,810 --> 00:58:40,337
- And it's far from the worst.
- Where is she? His mother?

787
00:58:40,514 --> 00:58:44,814
I don't know. If you find her, we got
a heap more files we could add to.

788
00:58:45,853 --> 00:58:47,445
Well, how many kids does she have?

789
00:58:47,621 --> 00:58:50,784
Least a dozen, probably. If not more.

790
00:58:50,958 --> 00:58:54,621
With her drug-arrest record, my guess
would be, she can't even remember.

791
00:58:54,795 --> 00:58:56,490
Can I see that?

792
00:59:00,968 --> 00:59:03,528
So we would need her permission,
right?

793
00:59:03,704 --> 00:59:08,368
No. Michael is a ward of the state.
Just apply and get a judge to sign off on it.

794
00:59:11,145 --> 00:59:15,241
