What it means is,
is that we wanna know...

845
01:03:30,151 --> 01:03:33,450
...if you would like to
become part of this family.

846
01:03:42,263 --> 01:03:44,128
Kind of thought I already was.

847
01:03:44,299 --> 01:03:46,494
[LAUGHS]

848
01:03:46,668 --> 01:03:48,260
[FAMILY LAUGHING]

849
01:03:52,974 --> 01:03:55,568
Well, all right, then.

850
