you're not covered by a defender.

866
01:05:02,277 --> 01:05:05,769
Now, I'll be the running back, and you
show me what you're supposed to do.

867
01:05:06,114 --> 01:05:07,513
Ready? Hike!

868
01:05:08,016 --> 01:05:11,884
You'll block him. He'll hit him.
Quarterback'll hand it off.

869
01:05:12,053 --> 01:05:13,918
He gets the ball, and he takes off!

870
01:05:14,089 --> 01:05:16,683
Open lane to the end zone.
All there is to it.

871
01:05:16,858 --> 01:05:18,120
What's going on here?

872
01:05:18,960 --> 01:05:20,621
Blended spice just scored.

873
01:05:20,795 --> 01:05:23,787
We were going through the playbook.
Michael got moved to offense.

874
01:05:23,965 --> 01:05:27,298
When you're done, put the players
back in the spice cabinet. Thank you.

875
01:05:27,469 --> 01:05:28,936
SJ:
No problem.

876
01:05:29,270 --> 01:05:33,001
Actually, Mom, we were
kind of waiting for you.

877
01:05:33,174 --> 01:05:35,108
You see,
the new Madden game came out...

878
01:05:35,276 --> 01:05:37,574
...and me and Michael
were wanting to go get it.

879
01:05:37,745 --> 01:05:41,374
- I can't, I've got a meeting in 10 minutes.
- But he can drive.

880
01:05:41,616 --> 01:05:43,379
He can drive us.

881
01:05:44,486 --> 01:05:46,010
[YOUNG MC'S "BUST A MOVE"
